# Starter monorepo

- Nx + pnpm at repo root. Apps: `apps/web` (Next.js), `apps/api` (NestJS), `libs/shared`.
- Full agent guide: `AGENTS.md`. Commands: `pnpm dev`, `pnpm test`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm lint`.
- Minimal scope: only change files required for the task. No drive-by refactors.
- Prisma 7: run `pnpm prisma:generate` after schema edits. Never commit `.env`.
- Do not create git commits unless the user asks.
